OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779207074
OL,3,CMan jailed for injuring 'defenceless'
OL,4,Cpensioner in unprovoked attack
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for injuring a
OL,7,F"defenceless" pensioner in an
OL,8,Funprovoked attack in Salisbury.
OL,10,FMorgan Rees, 21, from Middle Wallop in
OL,11,FHampshire, attacked the victim, who
OL,12,Fwas 85, on 25 January 2025 after
OL,13,Fpulling him out of his vehicle.
OL,15,FRees then kicked and punched the
OL,16,Fvictim, leaving him injured on the
OL,17,Fground, before getting into the
OL,18,Fdriver's seat and driving off.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
