OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779207074
OL,3,CMan jailed for injuring 'defenceless'
OL,4,Cpensioner in unprovoked attack
OL,6,FRees had been out drinking in
OL,7,FSalisbury before the attack, and had
OL,8,Fvarious disagreements with others
OL,9,Fbefore emptying bins and throwing
OL,10,Frubbish around the local area.
OL,12,FRees was sentenced to three years and
OL,13,Ffour months in prison on Monday (18
OL,14,FMay) after pleading guilty to Section
OL,15,F18 grevious bodily harm at Salisbury
OL,16,FCrown Court.
OL,18,FAs well as the prison sentence, Rees
OL,19,Fwas also disqualified from driving for
OL,20,F32 months and ordered to pay a #228
OL,21,Fsurcharge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779207074
OL,3,CMan jailed for injuring 'defenceless'
OL,4,Cpensioner in unprovoked attack
OL,6,FThe victim described how the attack
OL,7,Fhad affected him during a victim
OL,8,Fimpact statement read out in court.
OL,10,F"I cannot for the life of me
OL,11,Fcomprehend why this guy attacked me, I
OL,12,Fam a defenseless 85-year-old man who
OL,13,Fwas sat in my van minding my own
OL,14,Fbusiness.
OL,16,F"Not every day, but quite often, I
OL,17,Fthink about what happened to me that
OL,18,Fday.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
