OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779207074
OL,3,CMan jailed for injuring 'defenceless'
OL,4,Cpensioner in unprovoked attack
OL,6,F"Every time I shave my face and look
OL,7,Fin the mirror I have to always take
OL,8,Fcare of myself because of the damage
OL,9,Fthat was caused to my eye socket when
OL,10,FI was smacked on the side of the head,
OL,11,Fpulled out the van and kicked.
OL,13,F"The memory is not a dim one and is
OL,14,Fstill very real.
OL,16,F"It has frightened me off going to
OL,17,FSalisbury, or anywhere in the evening,
OL,18,Fon my own again."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
