PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779207074
OL,3,CMan jailed for injuring 'defenceless'
OL,4,Cpensioner in unprovoked attack
OL,6,FDet Sgt Emma Fisher, of South CID,
OL,7,Fsaid: "This was an unprovoked,
OL,8,Fprolonged attack on an innocent member
OL,9,Fof the public.
OL,11,F"The level of violence inflicted on
OL,12,Fhis victim by Rees is absolutely
OL,13,Funacceptable and I am pleased he has
OL,14,Fbeen jailed ` this sentence reflects
OL,15,Fthe severity of his actions and I hope
OL,16,Fit provides his victim with the
OL,17,Fopportunity to feel some form of
OL,18,Fclosure.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
