OL,3,CMan jailed for injuring 'defenceless'
OL,4,Cpensioner in unprovoked attack
OL,6,F"Violence of any kind will not be
OL,7,Ftolerated and we will seek to put
OL,8,Foffenders before the courts
OL,9,Fimmediately."
